Sierra Suites Software - AWS POC Assessment - Page 11 of 11CONCLUSIONThe Sierra Suites AI Platform represents a significant opportunity to transform constructionproject management through data-driven intelligence. Our comprehensive platforminfrastructure is production-ready, with 12 fully functional modules serving the completeproject lifecycle.This POC will transform our AI capabilities from demonstration features to production-gradeintelligence by:11. Training machine learning models on real construction data12. Embedding AI analysis directly into project workflows13. Providing measurable value through time and cost savings14. Validating the business model with pilot contractorsThe embedded Project Predictor feature is particularly innovative, bringing real-time AIintelligence directly to where project managers work, eliminating the friction of navigating toseparate AI tools. This integration ensures every project benefits from data-driven insightsautomatically.Expected Outcomes:• 50% of AI suite production-ready after POC• Proven ROI with documented savings of $30K-$95K per project• Competitive differentiation through data-driven intelligence• Foundation for Phase 2 expansion to remaining AI toolsWith AWS's expertise in machine learning and our deep understanding of constructionworkflows, this partnership will create the industry's most advanced AI-powered constructionmanagement platform, specifically designed for the underserved small-to-mid-sizedcontractor market.Next Steps15. AWS technical review and feedback16. POC credit approval ($25,000)17. Technical kickoff meeting18. Begin Phase 1 implementationEND OF POC ASSESSMENT